    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你要解开复杂艰深的对话谜题，查询恐怖阴谋的真相<br></li><li>你需要综合考虑事件解决、队伍预算和管理、普通群众对你们的评价等因素<br></li><li>你的选择会导致不同的结局<br></li><li>登场人物多达35人以上，他们拥有复杂又真实的个性<br></li><li>真人演出和应景的音乐给你带来真实的体验</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016770/extras/a67f32297a896e6c9113726dcd7af3ad.poster.avif?t=1728901217\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016770/extras/a67f32297a896e6c9113726dcd7af3ad.webm?t=1728901217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016770/extras/a67f32297a896e6c9113726dcd7af3ad.mp4?t=1728901217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏部分</strong></h2>为了检举恐怖组织“The Liberation Front”，你要管理有限的预算、和队伍成员一起收集情报，还要应付媒体的追问。然而事情不止是这些。<br><br>作为警探，你的任务是审问嫌疑人。你需要理解他们的背景和动机，才能有效地选择是用威胁还是哄骗又或者是同情共鸣来对付嫌疑人。这里面并没有什么万能的解决方案，而时间是不等人的……<br><br>你离真犯人越近，嫌疑人们的抵抗也越激烈，审讯也越难进行。你要靠复杂的对话和心理操作等技巧来查明真相。<br><br> “The Liberation Front”是没那么容易对付的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016770/extras/26144de163a98e7b0a523a354ff3301e.poster.avif?t=1728901217\" width=616 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016770/extras/26144de163a98e7b0a523a354ff3301e.webm?t=1728901217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016770/extras/26144de163a98e7b0a523a354ff3301e.mp4?t=1728901217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏目的</strong></h2>『Interrogation: You will be deceived』以恐怖行为，警察暴力，公民、国家、大企业之间的权力不平衡，等现代社会的各种问题为题材，是一款故事性极强的对话型解谜游戏。本作像『This War of Mine』『Papers Please』『This is the Police』以及『Orwell』等游戏一样，是向玩家的道德观和意识形态提出挑战，暴露现实社会问题的作品。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016770/extras/698dfeee781585740a3ab1d23cdf378c.poster.avif?t=1728901217\" width=616 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016770/extras/698dfeee781585740a3ab1d23cdf378c.webm?t=1728901217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1016770/extras/698dfeee781585740a3ab1d23cdf378c.mp4?t=1728901217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
